{"tid":407853,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦時裝周：設計新貴讓你看見陌生的英倫風","createTime":"2017-09-20T18:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T18:36:15.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4f8dc1e00cb27c0266630181562865003cc1d6","tid":407853,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/020037_a7f477623660a556894440160ca97375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F020037_a7f477623660a556894440160ca97375.jpg&h=f136da78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼於Central Saint Martins畢業後，這是Halpern舉行的第一場發布會，重要的是，只是第一場騷就被紐約奢侈品百貨公司Bergdorf Goodman選中，買入設計系列。雖然年輕設計師的名字總是很容易掀起熱潮，但只是如此短的時間就做到這個狀況，是不平凡的。<br />\n <br />\n閃閃生輝的系列以珠片貫穿，靈感是來至七十年代Disco的文化；剪裁偏富有女人味，如包裝紙的雕塑形狀站立於閃呤呤的連身褲之上，藝術感爆棚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fikupk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fikupk&d=dmzxkdd1Kkw2ixG9jwRT5CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=fcb120de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fikupk</a>"},{"pid":"4e681a51fc511747cdce216e2d8efa376591ae89","tid":407853,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"好走喇兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}